"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/posts/2576488119051989?__tn__=K-R</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家睇吓個 email 有無問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果無問題就廣傳一下 <br />\n諮詢最後今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[#官方資訊] 早前分享了一位高級政務官朋友就《逃犯條例》爭議的感受，得到數千轉載，迴響十分熱烈，也有不少公務員私訊回應。本頁對象一直以黃藍以外的專業人士為主，雖然平日只分享國際視野資訊，但在關鍵時刻，也希望為一些平日對社會抽離的朋友，提供更多資訊參考。以下是我的另一位AO朋友擔心局勢惡化，希望以自己的方式真正為特區政府服務，因此以私人身份草擬的意見書，回應特區政府選舉管理委員會關於區議會選舉的官方諮詢，並使用了完美官僚理據、格式和文法，就DQ候選人提供了詳細意見。根據官方資訊，《逃犯條例》收到4500份意見書，其中3000份「贊成」，因此發出意見書並非毫無價值。這位AO表示，大家可以直接使用這格式，根據個人觀點加減內容直接電郵遞交，因為香港人大家都忙，這過程只需一分鐘，應該最符合成本效益。截止日期是7月10日或之前，請廣傳，好人一生平安。<br />\n<br />\nEmail 喺入面 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/posts/2576488119051989?__tn__=K-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon%2Fposts%2F2576488119051989%3F__tn__%3DK-R&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1d%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=c4dc6649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/posts/2576488119051989?__tn__=K-R</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1299429/page/1?post=7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1299429/page/1?post=7</a><br />\n【DQ區選反對確認書】同我入黎填撚左佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1297868\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1297868</a><br />\n<br />\n[3000萬個火急] 一人一信反對區議會DQ機制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1284662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1284662</a><br />\n<br />\n一齊反DQ 各位巴打入嚟填咗佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1261560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1261560</a><br />\n<br />\n警告！！選管會取消公開咨詢唔代表撤回新DQ指引<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1257486/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1257486/</a><br />\n<br />\n一名香港市民，搞掂！唔該幫手推！ 【全民反DQ！】一人一信反對區議會選舉DQ參選人資格！7月10號截止<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1267161/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1267161/</a><br />\n<br />\n［重要］區議會選舉招募各路人馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1295057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1295057</a><br />\n<br />\n[急] 沈旭暉喺 facebook 出咗篇有關區議會選舉的官方諮詢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dgqHFT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dgqHFT</a>"},{"pid":"764ce53ba88984006b2672fa5409545836c0eec5","tid":1299504,"uid":119386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:18:29.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8769f7ccf28f3d7fcb669853264e4808cb216b36","tid":1299504,"uid":251086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"71abcd84f50fd34ba34f8c79c8f6b715827f3460","tid":1299504,"uid":76331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b098ac9e51e96316e8abba7db76776ec96a1f0ad","tid":1299504,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"8154cc8199a960c9f9a9e26a67937554f7b99902","tid":1299504,"uid":243883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:33:49.000Z","msg":"喺fb copy唔到段字點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6612c12b435edf8bf4fd0fd80029fca120eae96","tid":1299504,"uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:35:17.000Z","msg":"send"},{"pid":"1e54aa205f2ea026dcfd098f7559b1b92fce803a","tid":1299504,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:36:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bebf4768a6c35ca8cb18202277eeebda5974832","tid":1299504,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8154cc8199a960c9f9a9e26a67937554f7b99902","tid"